title: Undefeated Team ( 10:0 ) looking for Plat 2+ toplaner
body:
Hey guys, we are looking for a toplaner, who plays ap-heavy toplaner like vladimir, rumble, ryze and so on.
we are still undefeated and communicate with ts.
If u have a big championpool and know how to play apheavy toplaner then add me in game. 
Free Gape Horn
